topic.title: /Pol/ Game General Discussion
topic.body:
Sick and tired of the cucked game industry? Ever wanted to Play a game that's not pozzed? Can you help develop a game?
If so then this is where we will do it.

We will need to discuss many things.

>Gameplay
>Game Design
>Story
>Player and Game Models
>Sound and Music
>Voice acting

And more...
